findings.title: Re-initialization issue with pool
findings.description: The pool can be re-initialized again when there's enough FEI again, which is not the intention.

findings.title: Immutable variables not enforced
findings.description: Variables tokenSpent and tokenReceived are intended to be immutable but are not declared as such.

findings.title: Contract starts with a full buffer at deployment
findings.description: A contract that inherits from RateLimited starts out with a full buffer when it is deployed, which means the full bufferCap is immediately available after deployment.
